## Révocation du token [/logout]

### api/logout [POST]

Révoquer le token

+ Request 

    + Headers 

            Accept: application/json,
            Authorization: Bearer PUT_TOKEN_HERE
        

+ Response 204 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /

            
              
